name: blockchain/ethereum/pancakeswap/Pancakeswap Router Deployer
description:
Compiles and deploys a Pancake router contract.

Note, Pancace factory should be used together with a Pancake factory contract.

2dd1939f-cbcf-4bfd-9076-1bcf32623d5c.name: contract name
2dd1939f-cbcf-4bfd-9076-1bcf32623d5c.description: The name of the created contract. It must be a valid Solidity contract name (no spaces, special characters).

2ce2b32e-927f-41b3-bcab-d77769eb3da9.name: init parameters
2ce2b32e-927f-41b3-bcab-d77769eb3da9.description: Receives an address of an already deployed Pancace factory contract and an already deployed wrapped BNB contract.

c7708f4f-1b7d-4292-bdf6-a607378707b4.name: credentials
c7708f4f-1b7d-4292-bdf6-a607378707b4.description: Receives a private URL to a node provider and a private key for a blockchain account.

2b7af6d6-aa19-4c89-9cba-5c8b4a8f6fb0.name: events
2b7af6d6-aa19-4c89-9cba-5c8b4a8f6fb0.description: Muliplexed events. Use a Demultiplexer to separate them if needed.

c756affd-6db5-4293-920b-ed329630f3c6.name: source
c756affd-6db5-4293-920b-ed329630f3c6.description: The source of the deployed contract in single file form. Required if want to perform contract verification on blockchain explorers (e.g. etherscan).

27ebe7c3-33de-4485-ba68-e659a8581cd0.name: compile settings
27ebe7c3-33de-4485-ba68-e659a8581cd0.description:
The settings used to compile the contract, like solidiy version, optimization settings, etc.
These are required e.g. if you want to perform contract verification on blockchain explorers (e.g. etherscan).

86c83cbf-ac3a-4a4e-bab8-1578bbdcb5ba.name: error
86c83cbf-ac3a-4a4e-bab8-1578bbdcb5ba.description: Sends out any error that happened during compilation or deployment.

5571c387-c57c-4245-a36a-4c990523e6a6.name: maps init parameters values to array

a5e0dc15-3bc3-4221-8d47-c849560de805.name: query and set factory`s init hash
